---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Europe Itinerary Building | Custom Travel Plan Design | DURIAN"
  description="Build a credible, well structured Europe itinerary with route logic, accommodation alignment, and realistic timing. Personalised planning guidance."
  breadcrumb={[
    { name: 'Services', url: 'https://www.duriantravel.com/services/' },
    { name: 'Itinerary Building', url: 'https://www.duriantravel.com/services/itinerary-building/' }
  ]}
  keywords="Europe itinerary building, custom Europe travel plan, visa compliant itinerary, European travel custom design, itinerary structure"
>
  <section class="hero-sm hero-gradient">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label" style="color:var(--color-accent-light)">Service</span>
      <h1 class="hero-sm__title" style="color:white">Itinerary Building</h1>
      <p class="hero-sm__subtitle">Structure a visa-compliant travel plan that matches your documents and demonstrates genuine purpose.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <div class="service-content prose">
          <h2>Why Your Itinerary Matters</h2>
          <p>Your itinerary isn't just a list of cities — it's evidence. Consular officers use it to assess whether your trip makes sense, whether your finances match your plans, and whether you intend to return home.</p>

          <h2>What We Build Together</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Day-by-day travel plan aligned with your visa application</li>
            <li>Accommodation matching (hotel bookings, Airbnb, host letters)</li>
            <li>Transportation logic (flights, trains, buses between cities)</li>
            <li>Activity framework that supports your stated travel purpose</li>
            <li>Budget alignment with your financial proof</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <ol class="step-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Initial Consultation:</strong> We discuss your travel goals, budget, and any specific visa constraints you might have.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>First Draft:</strong> We build a logical route based on your entry/exit points and desired pace.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Accommodation Alignment:</strong> Each night is mapped to a specific hotel or area, ensuring there are no 'gaps' that could lead to a visa refusal.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Final Refinement:</strong> We add daily activities and transportation details to create a robust, credible travel document.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <h2>Who Is This For?</h2>
          <p>This service is ideal for first-time Schengen applicants, travelers with complex multi-country plans, or anyone who has previously faced a refusal due to 'unclear purpose of stay'.</p>

          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <dl class="service-faq">
            <dt>Do you book the hotels for me?</dt>
            <dd>No, DURIAN is a consultancy. We provide the structure and guidance on which hotels to book to match your itinerary, but the actual bookings remain under your control.</dd>
            
            <dt>Will this guarantee my visa?</dt>
            <dd>No service can guarantee a visa outcome. However, a well-structured itinerary significantly reduces the risk of refusal based on 'logic' or 'credibility' issues.</dd>
            
            <dt>Can you help with flights too?</dt>
            <dd>We help you plan the logical flow of your flights (which cities to fly in and out of), but we do not handle ticket purchases.</dd>
          </dl>

          <div class="notice notice--warning"><span>⚠️</span><p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This is educational guidance. We do not book travel or guarantee visa outcomes.</p></div>
        </div>

        <aside class="service-sidebar">
          <div class="price-card">
            <span class="price-card__label">Investment</span>
            <span class="price-card__price">€24</span>
            <span class="price-card__detail">Itinerary review + structure plan</span>
            <a href="/free-visa-audit/" class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;margin-top:var(--space-4)">Start with Free Audit →</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.hero-sm { padding-block: var(--space-16); }
.hero-sm__title { font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl)); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
.hero-sm__subtitle { font-size: var(--text-lg); color: hsl(150 30% 75%); max-width: 52ch; line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); }
.service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: var(--space-12); align-items: start; }
@media (max-width: 860px) { .service-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.price-card { background: white; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: var(--space-8); text-align: center; position: sticky; top: 100px; }
.price-card__label { display: block; font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: var(--font-semibold); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
.price-card__price { display: block; font-size: var(--text-5xl); font-weight: var(--font-extrabold); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
.price-card__detail { display: block; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); }

/* Service specific styles */
.step-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-block: var(--space-8); counter-reset: steps; }
.step-list li { position: relative; padding-left: var(--space-12); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); line-height: 1.6; }
.step-list li::before { content: counter(steps); counter-increment: steps; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--color-navy); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; }
.service-faq dt { font-weight: var(--font-bold); color: var(--color-navy); margin-top: var(--space-6); font-size: var(--text-base); }
.service-faq dd { margin-left: 0; margin-top: var(--space-2); color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.6; }
</style>
